## 🚨 CRITICAL DIRECTIVE

**This teaching MUST run before any other teachings are processed.**

If this teaching is not applied and verified, your spoke cannot reliably adopt future teachings. The entire framework depends on this working.

**Action Required:**
1. Auto-adopt this teaching immediately (safe_to_auto_adopt: true)
2. Run the audit (Step 3 below)
3. Confirm all processed teachings are actually adopted
4. Only then process other pending teachings

**If audit fails:** Do NOT proceed with other teachings. Contact hub or resolve failures first.

